<plot>Amezcua (Eleazr Garcia Jr.) is a corrupt police officer who recruits petty criminals for kidnappings in Mexico City. 'La Banda del Antrax,' his latest production, is in the midst of kidnapping a young female executive in order to collect a large ransom. However, he runs into a few setbacks when another officer, Solis (Miguel Angel Rodríguez) starts investigating this kidnapping.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?305657</url></doc>
